<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.2">
<l>vēta mutalvaṉ viḷaṅku purinūlaṉ</l>
<l>pātam paravip palarum paṇintētti</l>
<l>kātaṉmai ceyyuṅkaṇ ṇapurat temperumāṉ</l>
<l>tātu naṟuntuḻāy tāḻntūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, alight and sip the honeyed, fragrant tulasī</l>
<l>On the primal [lord] of the Vedas, the one with the bright twisted thread,</l>
<l>Our great lord in Kaṇṇapuram where many perform devotions,</l>
<l>Praising [him], bowing, and adoring his feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
